#: resources/views/edit/link-child-to-family.phtml
msgid ""
"A child may have more than one set of parents. The relationship between the "
"child and the parents can be biological, legal, or based on local culture "
"and tradition. If no pedigree is specified, then a biological relationship "
"will be assumed."
msgstr ""
"Mwǎna akokí kozala na míngi koleka limbalé lya babóti. Mokangano káti na "
"mwǎna na babóti ekokí kozala ya makilá mɔ̌kɔ́, ya lɛ́ta tǒ na ntína ya bizaleli "
"bya bonkɔ́kɔ.Sɔ́kí libótá litíyámí tɛ́, mokangano mwa makilá mɔ̌kɔ́ ndé ekopɔnama."

#. I18N: Description of a “Data fix” module
