#: resources/views/help/media-object.phtml
msgid ""
"A media object is a record in the family tree which contains information "
"about a media file. This information may include a title, a copyright "
"notice, a transcript, privacy restrictions, etc. The media file, such as the "
"photo or video, can be stored locally (on this webserver) or remotely (on a "
"different webserver)."
msgstr ""
"Elɔ́kɔ ya bopanzi nsango ezalí bokɔ́tisi na nzeté ya libótá boye ezalí na "
"nsango ya kásá-kásá ya bopanzi nsango. Nsango eye ekokí kozala na mokonza, "
"nkomá ya copyright, nkomá, bokáti ndelo bwa maye matálí bato, etc. Kásá-kásá "
"ya bopanzi nsango, lokóla elílí tǒ video, ekokí kobátelama na ndáko (na "
"webserver eye) tǒ mosíká (na webserver ekɛsɛ́ní)."

